WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:06.000
Subtitles by DramaFever

00:53.390 --> 01:00.880
<i>[Although inspired by true events,
the characters and cases are fictional.]</i>

01:00.880 --> 01:04.849
<i>[Measures were taken when filming the
episode to ensure the mental well-being]</i>

01:04.849 --> 01:08.890
<i>[of the minor actor, and such measures
will continue after the filming.]</i>

01:08.890 --> 01:11.450
This is Kang Kwon Joo at
the Poongsan Golden Time Team.

01:11.450 --> 01:14.080
My daughter left this morning
to go to school.

01:14.080 --> 01:17.630
<i>She texted me that
the scumbag kidnapped her.</i>

01:17.630 --> 01:22.610
We checked her location through an app,
and her cell phone was near his house...

01:22.610 --> 01:27.000
<i>And my husband took a knife
and ran to that scumbag's house.</i>

01:27.000 --> 01:30.010
Scumbag? Can you please explain?

01:34.200 --> 01:36.620
The caller's name is Oh Soon Im. Age 45.

01:36.620 --> 01:39.970
She runs a fish shop at Poongsan Fish
Market with her husband, Hwang Ki Hyuk.

01:39.970 --> 01:43.620
They have a daughter, Hee Joo, 18.
And a son, Ji Wook, 7.

01:45.180 --> 01:49.390
Director Kang, Hee Joo's
a victim of child rape.

01:49.390 --> 01:51.600
The offender was released a month ago.

01:51.600 --> 01:54.940
After passing the teaching exam,
he got drunk and raped the child.

01:54.940 --> 01:57.280
Being that it was his first offense,
and it was six years ago

01:57.280 --> 01:59.500
he must have gotten off easy.

01:59.500 --> 02:02.250
Hee Joo is a victim of child rape,
registered for police protection.

02:02.250 --> 02:03.640
<i>Is that right?</i>

02:07.810 --> 02:10.820
I'm sure they're hiding something.

02:10.820 --> 02:14.060
Yes, she is a victim of child rape.

02:14.860 --> 02:17.440
Oh my goodness, child rape?

02:17.440 --> 02:22.480
So please find our Hee Joo for us.
And please find my husband, too.

02:22.480 --> 02:25.770
Director, we've located
Hee Joo's last cell phone signal.

02:25.770 --> 02:30.030
4-45 Hope Villa in Hwai-dong,
near Yum Gi Tae's residence.

02:30.030 --> 02:31.680
The phone is turned off.

02:31.680 --> 02:35.100
See where she went after leaving home,
and check the CCTV by Yum Gi Tae's home.

02:35.100 --> 02:37.960
And track his anklet
to see where he was this morning.

02:37.960 --> 02:39.460
Yes, Ma'am.

02:40.000 --> 02:41.330
This is a code zero situation.

02:41.330 --> 02:43.530
Caller's name is Oh Soo Nim. Age 45.

02:43.530 --> 02:46.200
Her daughter, Hwang Hee Joo,
was raped six years ago.

02:46.200 --> 02:49.270
Believing the offender kidnapped her,
she says her husband, Hwang Ki Hyuk

02:49.270 --> 02:52.030
went to the offender
Yum Gi Tae's home with a knife.

02:52.030 --> 02:54.980
Hwang Hee Joo's phone
was last located near Yum Gi Tae's home.

02:54.980 --> 02:56.300
This may be his revenge.

02:56.300 --> 02:59.750
Detective Park, please go to
3-45 Hope Villa, Hwai Street, Hwadong-gu

02:59.750 --> 03:01.410
Yum Gi Tae's residence.

03:01.410 --> 03:04.510
Detective Koo, please go to Gyeyoung
Station and the Poongsan Fish Market.

03:04.510 --> 03:06.690
Yes, we're heading over.

03:06.690 --> 03:09.820
In case of emergency, Hwai Station,
please have a backup team.

03:09.820 --> 03:13.910
All officers, please wear bulletproof
vests and gloves, and stay safe.

03:13.910 --> 03:16.060
Send out an alert
for the code zero situation.

03:16.060 --> 03:17.400
Yes.

03:17.400 --> 03:20.690
The court has control
over the tracking of GPS anklets

03:20.690 --> 03:22.960
- so it may take some time.
- Do it ASAP.

03:22.960 --> 03:26.370
Ma'am, anything we should know
about following the offender's release?

03:26.370 --> 03:31.150
<i>Actually, he came
to our store a few days ago.</i>

03:31.150 --> 03:34.150
- Pardon?
- I was going to the freezer in the back.

03:34.150 --> 03:37.550
<i>And I saw someone looking
into our store from the back door.</i>

03:37.550 --> 03:40.540
- Who are you?
- He was wearing muddy shoes.

03:40.740 --> 03:42.930
Honey! Honey!

03:42.930 --> 03:44.690
Honey!

03:46.100 --> 03:49.700
Mister, I came to ask Hee Joo
for her forgiveness.

03:49.700 --> 03:51.950
I've done her wrong.

03:51.950 --> 03:54.690
You bastard, how dare you come here?

03:57.740 --> 04:02.050
What are you up to now?
How dare you!

04:02.050 --> 04:03.320
No!

04:03.320 --> 04:05.450
No...

04:05.450 --> 04:07.620
Honey, don't!
You better leave now!

04:07.620 --> 04:10.290
If you come back, I'll kill you.

04:10.290 --> 04:13.010
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

04:13.010 --> 04:14.900
I'm sorry.

04:14.900 --> 04:17.000
How dare he come here...

04:19.420 --> 04:21.500
Come on, call the cops!

04:21.500 --> 04:25.040
<i>And that night, Hee Joo...</i>

04:31.640 --> 04:34.270
Hee Joo, what are you doing?

04:34.270 --> 04:35.830
Honey! What are you doing?

04:35.830 --> 04:39.840
- Let go!
- Hee Joo...

04:39.840 --> 04:44.070
- This way, he won't recognize me.
- What do you mean?

04:44.070 --> 04:49.010
He was waiting for me
by our school.

04:49.010 --> 04:52.890
He was hiding behind the entrance,
and he was staring at me!

04:52.890 --> 04:56.080
- What?
- That damn bastard.

05:09.840 --> 05:12.290
This is all your fault!

05:12.290 --> 05:15.570
You said you would make sure
he never comes out!

05:15.570 --> 05:21.800
I'll go crazy knowing that he's back out!

05:25.040 --> 05:26.630
Get out!

05:26.630 --> 05:31.180
I can't stand the sight of you! Get out!

05:31.180 --> 05:32.870
Get out!

05:35.120 --> 05:37.560
Close the door.

05:37.560 --> 05:40.910
<i>My husband believed
he had come back to get revenge.</i>

05:40.910 --> 05:43.300
<i>We went to the police to ask for help</i>

05:43.300 --> 05:46.200
but they just gave us a little watch
kind of thing, and told us to wait.

05:47.600 --> 05:50.580
And this happened!

05:50.580 --> 05:54.110
<i>Please, save Hee Joo and my husband.</i>

05:54.110 --> 05:57.270
It's been verified Hwang Ki Hyuk
entered Yum Gi Tae's house a minute ago.

05:57.270 --> 06:01.400
But it looks like Yum Gi Tae hasn't
come out of his house since last night.

06:02.790 --> 06:07.380
<i>- The evil...
- Hold on.</i>

06:07.380 --> 06:17.590
<i>like the burdens of a cross,
hardships of a life...</i>

06:17.590 --> 06:22.230
<i>My only wish...</i>

06:22.230 --> 06:23.990
You bastard!

06:23.990 --> 06:25.610
Hee Joo!

06:25.610 --> 06:27.310
Move!

06:27.310 --> 06:29.510
Hee Joo! Hee Joo!

06:30.640 --> 06:33.300
Where is she? Where is she, you bastard?

06:33.300 --> 06:34.910
What did you do to her?

06:34.910 --> 06:37.750
What are you saying?
Why would Hee Joo be here?

06:37.750 --> 06:42.240
Hee Joo texted us saying
that you kidnapped her.

06:42.240 --> 06:46.610
You psycho bastard, where is Hee Joo?
What have you done to her now?

06:46.610 --> 06:49.550
I don't know what you are talking about.

06:49.550 --> 06:53.600
- Please put the knife down.
- You think you can fool me again?

06:53.600 --> 06:58.700
If you even laid a finger
on my daughter, I'll kill you!

06:58.700 --> 07:01.860
<i>[10:05 a.m., 5 minutes after
the murder attempt of rapist Yum Gi Tae]</i>

07:01.860 --> 07:04.680
<i>[Episode 3: Judgment Time]</i>

07:04.680 --> 07:09.940
<i>[To sin is a human business, but
to justify sins is a devilish business.]</i>

07:09.940 --> 07:13.900
<i>[Tolstoy]</i>

07:14.770 --> 07:18.290
<i>[10:07 a.m., 7 minutes after
the murder attempt of rapist Yum Gi Tae]</i>

07:19.850 --> 07:21.660
- Are you sure?
- Of course.

07:21.660 --> 07:26.290
As I said, he's an expert on cars.
And a computer whiz, too.

07:26.290 --> 07:32.690
He posted the blueprint
of that device on the website "Stab."

07:32.690 --> 07:36.670
The more I find out about Kwak Min Soo,
the more suspicious I get--

07:36.670 --> 07:37.740
- Hey.
- Yes?

07:37.740 --> 07:41.420
- Why was he absent that day?
- I didn't have enough time to find out.

07:41.420 --> 07:45.420
I'm finding that out now.
Just so I can get him...

07:45.420 --> 07:48.420
I think I've met everyone in Poongsan.

07:48.420 --> 07:52.150
You should give me some recognition, no?

07:52.150 --> 07:57.960
Come on, you're not going to praise me?

08:02.280 --> 08:04.370
You think you'll get away with this?

08:06.790 --> 08:10.070
<i>Similar build and age...
Is it him?</i>

08:12.390 --> 08:15.530
- Kwak Min Soo, you bastard!
- Kang Woo!

08:16.970 --> 08:18.530
You...

08:27.290 --> 08:29.140
Stop right there, bastard!

08:29.710 --> 08:32.570
What did I ever do...

08:32.570 --> 08:35.010
Hey, Kwak Min Soo!

08:35.020 --> 08:37.429
Kang Woo, please...

08:37.740 --> 08:40.309
Kang Woo!

08:44.940 --> 08:46.680
Kwak Min Soo!

08:54.050 --> 08:55.880
Stop right there, bastard.

09:02.880 --> 09:05.120
Are you okay?

09:10.300 --> 09:12.740
Dok Ki, go that way.

09:24.180 --> 09:25.700
<i>- What the heck...</i>
- Sorry.

09:33.180 --> 09:35.510
Bastard.

09:38.110 --> 09:41.000
- It's you?
- He's not here.

09:41.800 --> 09:44.040
Go search everywhere!

09:44.680 --> 09:48.140
- Captain Do's not picking up his phone.
- Try the radio.

09:48.890 --> 09:51.980
I don't think he has a radio.

10:08.490 --> 10:13.740
Where were you on June 2nd?
Look me in the face!

10:13.740 --> 10:15.680
You know me, right?

10:15.680 --> 10:18.170
- What the heck are you saying?
- Stop.

10:37.250 --> 10:41.760
- Damn it...
- Are you okay?

10:41.760 --> 10:43.620
What took you so long, jerk?

10:43.620 --> 10:44.710
No...

10:44.710 --> 10:47.830
- Captain Koo, where are you?
- You have a radio?

10:47.830 --> 10:50.730
- No, she gave me one...
- You idiot.

10:50.730 --> 10:52.890
How can you say that to me?

10:52.890 --> 10:56.200
- It's an emergency.
- Give that to me.

10:57.100 --> 10:59.800
This is more urgent.
Track a cab for me.

10:59.800 --> 11:02.990
Plate number 31-501.

11:04.230 --> 11:07.100
The passenger is an officer
from Opo Station, Kwak Min Soo.

11:07.100 --> 11:09.590
He may be the main culprit
in the case from three years ago.

11:09.590 --> 11:12.600
<i>Agent Jin, track the cab and
Officer Kwak Min Soo from Opo.</i>

11:12.600 --> 11:13.680
<i>Sure.</i>

11:13.680 --> 11:18.160
If you ever go off on your own again,
you'll go immediately back to jail.

11:18.160 --> 11:24.240
- Don't forget it.
- Do you enjoy threatening people?

11:25.100 --> 11:27.200
It's a warning.

11:28.390 --> 11:30.860
A child rapist from
six years ago was released

11:30.860 --> 11:33.100
and we received report
that he kidnapped the victim.

11:33.100 --> 11:36.350
The victim's last cell phone location
was at the suspect's villa.

11:36.350 --> 11:39.740
The victim's father went into
the suspect's villa with a knife.

11:45.480 --> 11:47.490
Damn.

11:47.490 --> 11:49.590
Dok Ki, go after him!

11:54.020 --> 11:55.990
She must have been raped
when she was young.

11:55.990 --> 12:00.420
- Oh my goodness...
- After he was released, this happened...

12:05.390 --> 12:07.750
- Mrs. Oh Soo Nim?
- Yes, that's me.

12:09.100 --> 12:10.800
I'm Detective Koo
from the Golden Time Team.

12:10.800 --> 12:12.950
Are my daughter
and husband safe?

12:12.950 --> 12:16.680
Your husband went into Yum's home,
and we sent a dispatch team out there.

12:16.720 --> 12:19.110
Your daughter left for school
and was kidnapped?

12:19.110 --> 12:21.170
- Yes.
- I need to check the text message.

12:26.600 --> 12:29.300
We'll trace her way to school,
and figure out the kidnapping site.

12:29.300 --> 12:33.100
I'll go too.
I know the exact way Hee Joo takes.

12:34.100 --> 12:36.600
We are here at Poongsan Fish Market.

12:36.600 --> 12:39.310
We're on the move with the caller
after confirming the text message.

12:44.950 --> 12:48.630
According to the guard, two members
from a nearby church were visiting.

12:48.630 --> 12:51.360
- The door was locked, so...
- Captain Do's not there, yet?

12:52.840 --> 12:55.720
Speak of the devil, he's here.

12:55.720 --> 12:58.700
Don't you know that
time is of the essence here?

12:58.700 --> 13:02.810
What are you doing here, Detective Yang?
Chief Na sent you to watch over me?

13:02.810 --> 13:05.050
- What are you saying...
- We have no time for this.

13:05.050 --> 13:08.670
Since it's your first day,
I'll lead the way.

13:08.670 --> 13:11.150
- Is there another entrance?
- No, that's the only one.

13:11.150 --> 13:13.940
The three of us will go first,
so come in behind us.

13:13.940 --> 13:18.560
Get a few officers to search the area,
and find Hee Joo and her phone.

13:18.560 --> 13:21.680
- Yes.
- There are possibly three hostages.

13:21.680 --> 13:26.800
Hwang Ki Hyuk is very angry
right now, so be careful.

13:28.140 --> 13:31.720
<i>Captain, please turn on your radio
so we can hear everything.</i>

13:31.720 --> 13:34.330
You should just come out
here yourself then.

13:34.330 --> 13:37.800
I never went to her school,
nor do I want revenge.

13:37.800 --> 13:40.390
All I did was visit your store.

13:40.390 --> 13:42.240
You're lying again!

13:42.240 --> 13:45.500
I know you did it. Where is she?

13:45.500 --> 13:52.080
He was praying with us, he's repented,
and he's never drank since that day.

13:52.080 --> 13:57.190
Think about it, if something
happens to Hee Joo

13:57.190 --> 13:58.940
I would become the suspect.

13:58.940 --> 14:00.730
Why would I do such a thing?

14:00.730 --> 14:07.010
I have this around my ankle
that tracks my location.

14:07.010 --> 14:09.940
It will show where I was
at the time Hee Joo went missing.

14:09.940 --> 14:11.810
Bastard!

14:11.810 --> 14:14.480
Shut your mouth!

14:18.400 --> 14:22.410
I know you're lying! Where is she?

14:28.990 --> 14:33.490
Police! Calm down
and put the knife on the floor.

14:37.830 --> 14:40.560
Police?
Why are you aiming that at me?

14:41.700 --> 14:44.260
This jerk kidnapped my daughter!

14:44.260 --> 14:46.860
- Hwang Hee Joo's not here.
- Please help me...

14:46.860 --> 14:49.240
You are mistaken.

14:49.240 --> 14:54.420
I don't remember what happened that day,
but I really want to apologize...

14:54.420 --> 14:57.870
I will never do anything to her again!

14:59.060 --> 15:02.880
<i>Both men are telling the truth.</i>

15:02.880 --> 15:04.890
<i>What's going on?</i>

15:05.650 --> 15:09.140
Captain, I believe
both men are telling the truth.

15:09.140 --> 15:11.820
- The truth?
- Yes, I know.

15:11.820 --> 15:15.420
I understand, but drop the knife.
You heard that Hee Joo's not here.

15:15.430 --> 15:18.300
She wasn't captured on the CCTV
in front of the house, either.

15:18.300 --> 15:22.790
Don't lie to me!
Hee Joo was kidnapped by him.

15:22.790 --> 15:25.200
She texted saying he kidnapped her.

15:25.200 --> 15:29.820
If anything happens to her,
I'll kill you all first!

15:33.390 --> 15:37.680
<i>He's completely worked up,
he may really end up killing Yum Gi Tae.</i>

15:37.680 --> 15:39.190
<i>I need to calm him down.</i>

15:39.190 --> 15:43.190
We just received information
on the GPS anklet.

15:43.190 --> 15:47.260
It's been verified Yum Gi Tae's
been home since yesterday morning.

15:53.200 --> 15:56.510
Oh, that's Hee Joo's keychain.

15:59.330 --> 16:02.510
<i>- Director, something's odd.
- Odd?</i>

16:02.510 --> 16:06.040
She may not have been kidnapped.

16:06.040 --> 16:07.130
What do you mean?

16:07.130 --> 16:08.650
<i>We've sent you the CCTV footage.</i>

16:08.650 --> 16:12.270
<i>A student resembling Hee Joo was seen
heading towards the bus terminal.</i>

16:12.270 --> 16:14.640
<i>Her mother says the keychain
hanging from the bag</i>

16:14.640 --> 16:17.090
<i>looks like the one she received
from a friend before.</i>

16:17.090 --> 16:20.470
<i>And a truck vendor in front
of the store says she saw Hee Joo.</i>

16:20.470 --> 16:22.870
- Have you seen her?
- Yes.

16:25.700 --> 16:27.490
What's wrong with you?

16:27.490 --> 16:30.250
Don't put your hand on me!

16:31.710 --> 16:37.090
It was after school started,
but she went towards the bus terminal.

16:43.390 --> 16:45.920
Then the one on the film here
may be Hee Joo.

16:51.700 --> 16:52.790
This is the call center.

16:52.790 --> 16:57.150
We have footage of Hee Joo going
towards the bus terminal at 9:30 a.m.

16:57.150 --> 17:01.150
And around 8:40 a.m., we have
footage of her near Hope Villa.

17:01.150 --> 17:06.099
It seems she went to Hwai after leaving
home, then went to the bus terminal.

17:06.099 --> 17:10.480
We suspect Hee Joo may have plotted
this to send Yum Gi Tae back to prison.

17:10.480 --> 17:14.579
Sir, please calm down.
Hee Joo is probably safe.

17:14.579 --> 17:20.170
- We spotted her somewhere else.
- Then you are saying she lied?

17:20.170 --> 17:25.569
How can you cops
only side with this bastard?

17:25.569 --> 17:27.990
You call yourselves police?

17:27.990 --> 17:34.490
Sir, we have video footage of Hee Joo
heading towards the bus terminal.

17:34.490 --> 17:37.340
- If you would like, we can show you.
- What?

17:45.500 --> 17:49.650
You think I'll believe you?

17:49.650 --> 17:55.410
<i>If you keep this up, I'll kill him.</i>

17:55.410 --> 18:00.050
Director, we've told him Hee Joo's safe,
but he won't believe us.

18:00.050 --> 18:01.660
<i>What do we do?</i>

18:01.660 --> 18:07.480
<i>He's ready to stab Yum Gi Tae.
I need to find a way to calm him down.</i>

18:11.890 --> 18:14.370
The next bullet is for you,
Mr. Hwang Ki Hyuk.

18:14.690 --> 18:17.140
It's been found that
Hee Joo plotted all this.

18:17.140 --> 18:23.570
You think if you take this chance
to kill him, you'll be able to relax?

18:23.570 --> 18:25.100
No.

18:26.500 --> 18:28.210
You are mistaken.

18:29.820 --> 18:31.850
Shut up!

18:31.850 --> 18:36.700
You know nothing about
the pain we went through, so shut up.

18:37.500 --> 18:40.270
You don't know anything!

18:41.500 --> 18:43.890
He's ruined my daughter!

18:43.890 --> 18:45.100
No!

18:45.100 --> 18:48.690
If you kill him here...

18:50.100 --> 18:52.950
Hee Joo will become a murderer's child.

18:55.350 --> 18:58.430
You have no idea what that's like.

19:02.030 --> 19:06.630
She'll live every day thinking that
she may become a monster.

19:07.310 --> 19:10.410
Even if that jerk deserves
to be ripped to pieces...

19:12.100 --> 19:17.000
Even if Hee Joo asked
you to kill him for her...

19:20.610 --> 19:22.500
If you are Hee Joo's father...

19:23.890 --> 19:26.340
If you truly love her...

19:30.890 --> 19:33.390
You need to stop here.

19:49.730 --> 19:51.680
Over there!
That's Hee Joo, right?

19:51.680 --> 19:54.330
- Yes.
- We've found Hee Joo.

19:54.330 --> 19:55.500
Hee Joo!

19:56.320 --> 19:59.040
When you meet Hee Joo,
make her audible to everyone.

19:59.040 --> 20:01.340
What are you doing here?

20:01.340 --> 20:05.270
<i>You know what mess you've created?</i>

20:05.270 --> 20:12.220
<i>Your dad has gone to his home.</i>

20:13.890 --> 20:15.330
<i>What?</i>

20:15.330 --> 20:18.100
<i>Why did Dad go to his house?</i>

20:44.410 --> 20:47.140
Mr. Hwang Ki Hyuk,
you are under arrest for trespassing

20:47.140 --> 20:49.600
causing bodily harm,
and for property damage.

20:49.600 --> 20:53.500
You have the right to an attorney,
and the right to defend yourself.

20:53.500 --> 20:55.130
<i>Let's go.</i>

21:00.630 --> 21:05.780
- My goodness, blood...
- I'm fine.

21:05.780 --> 21:08.100
I'm at fault here.

21:12.500 --> 21:15.740
Detective.

21:16.410 --> 21:18.710
Thank you for saving my life.

21:18.710 --> 21:26.950
God must have had mercy on me
seeing how earnestly I prayed.

21:28.690 --> 21:30.600
Stop your crap.

21:31.390 --> 21:34.760
The victim and her family haven't
forgiven you, so you're not forgiven.

21:36.690 --> 21:39.190
If you really want to be forgiven...

21:39.190 --> 21:44.480
suffer more than them,
and live your life in hell, got that?

21:51.200 --> 21:52.770
