22:15.920 --> 22:17.390
<i>Rhinitis?</i>

22:17.390 --> 22:21.050
<i>Then he would have a nasal voice
due to stuffed passageway.</i>

22:21.050 --> 22:24.600
<i>But he sounds like he's holding
his breath because of a bad smell.</i>

22:24.600 --> 22:28.020
Captain Do, is there
