23:01.780 --> 23:04.190
I shouldn't complain, I deserve it.

23:05.020 --> 23:06.510
What's that red thing?

23:06.510 --> 23:11.060
Oh, it's cotton I used
to clean up a wound.

23:14.100 --> 23:16.310
