23:22.780 --> 23:27.940
You'll need to come with us too
so you can give your testimony.

23:29.600 --> 23:32.020
Thank you, detectives.

23:32.020 --> 23:37.360
I'm sorry I caused a mess, I pray
God's blessings be with you, thank you.

23:37.360 --> 23:39.560
Yes, amen.

23:41.500 --> 23:47.000
- Please be strong.
- Thank you.

23:47.000 --> 23:51.610
<i>That's odd, it sounded like he was
holding his breath because of a stench.</i>

23:53.600 --> 23:56.100
<i>I'll play with...</i>

23:56.100 --> 24:00.930
<i>It's a child's voice.
Am I mistaken again?</i>

24:00.930 --> 24:04.490
<i>Yeah, there wouldn't be
a child in that house.</i>

24:04.490 --> 24:06.980
<i>I'm sure it was a sound
from outside the house.</i>

24:08.890 --> 24:11.600
Agent Park, please
look into something for me.

24:13.730 --> 24:17.100
We're heading to Poongsan now.

24:17.100 --> 24:21.560
