is a complete idiot.

24:21.560 --> 24:25.520
You heard him fire that shot, right?

24:26.600 --> 24:29.030
Thank you, come on in now.

24:29.030 --> 24:30.470
<i>Sure.</i>

24:30.470 --> 24:32.600
Let me know when you find it.

24:33.290 --> 24:36.590
