26:42.200 --> 26:43.670
How?

26:48.080 --> 26:50.720
What about the pain inside?

26:52.690 --> 26:58.070
How can I forget
when my heart still aches?

26:58.070 --> 27:00.280
How?

27:01.630 --> 27:03.590
<i>How...</i>

27:04.270 --> 27:09.750
I think Hee Joo and her dad are
suffering from anxiety disorder and ODD.

27:09.750 --> 27:14.680
