27:20.830 --> 27:24.170
How could she think that
such a lie would work?

27:26.000 --> 27:31.000
I understand why they call
rape victims "survivors."

27:31.000 --> 27:36.070
She'll have to heal from the wounds
in order to live the rest of her life.

27:41.460 --> 27:44.500
The case has been solved.
I don't know why I still feel so uneasy.

27:51.390 --> 27:53.650
Yeah, Dok Ki. What happened?

27:53.650 --> 27:57.970
<i>Kang Woo, I followed Kwak Min Soo
after he got off the cab</i>

27:57.970 --> 28:00.610
but he disappeared suddenly.

28:00.610 --> 28:03.530
<i>- Trying to escape as a ship stowaway.</i>
- Escape?

28:03.530 --> 28:06.980
<i>- Yes, what should I do?
- Move the car!</i>

28:06.990 --> 28:08.790
Find out the boat schedule.

28:08.790 --> 28:12.160
Search his motel room
to find any clues you can.

28:12.160 --> 28:13.580
Okay.

28:13.580 --> 28:15.830
I'm moving!

28:15.830 --> 28:18.070
He disappeared as soon as
he got off the cab.

28:18.070 --> 28:24.490
If Kwak Min Soo escapes,
our case is finished.

28:32.600 --> 28:36.220
- They're not picking up?
- My sister has a doctor appointment.

28:36.220 --> 28:38.260
I forgot.

28:40.100 --> 28:44.010
Ji Wook, I'll go bring an umbrella.
Wait here, okay?

28:44.010 --> 28:46.040
I'll take you home.

28:48.970 --> 28:52.810
