I can go by myself!

28:59.710 --> 29:01.640
Ji Wook!

29:01.770 --> 29:03.440
Ji Wook!

29:07.780 --> 29:11.470
Ji Wook! Invincible Watch!

29:14.540 --> 29:17.130
Ji Wook was able to defeat the monster

29:17.130 --> 29:22.100
and live happily ever after
with his mom, dad, and sister.

29:41.520 --> 29:43.100
Detective.

29:50.800 --> 29:54.480
What are you waiting for?
Apologize to Dad.

30:00.190 --> 30:03.550
Honey, don't do that to Hee Joo.

30:03.550 --> 30:05.220
She didn't do anything wrong.

30:05.220 --> 30:06.760
It's all my fault.

30:06.760 --> 30:10.130
I'm glad you know that.
You ruined everything.

30:10.130 --> 30:13.490
- How can you say that to your dad?
- What did I do?

30:13.490 --> 30:16.100
Dad ruined everything.

30:16.100 --> 30:19.970
If he had left it to the cops,
he would have gone back to jail.

30:20.690 --> 30:26.030
- Or just kill him and go to jail.
- What's wrong with you?

30:26.030 --> 30:29.290
How can you hurt us like this?

30:29.290 --> 30:30.890
Why are you hitting me?

30:30.890 --> 30:33.090
Stop acting like you're hurt.

30:34.800 --> 30:37.280
Nobody here hurts more than I do.

30:38.340 --> 30:42.670
No matter how much I try
to forget it, I can't forget it!

30:45.500 --> 30:48.520
You know what kind
of a jerk he is, too.

30:48.520 --> 30:51.090
I should have just died then.

30:51.090 --> 30:54.100
I would rather be dead
than live like this!

30:54.100 --> 30:57.480
How can you say that?

30:57.480 --> 30:59.470
You wicked girl.

30:59.470 --> 31:03.750
How dare you...

31:03.750 --> 31:05.110
That's enough.

31:06.800 --> 31:10.780
I can stay here alone,
so take Hee Joo and go home.

31:12.310 --> 31:16.990
She probably hasn't eaten all day.

31:17.620 --> 31:20.370
Get her something to eat.

31:20.370 --> 31:24.310
Ji Wook will be home soon, too.
Come on, go.

31:26.080 --> 31:28.410
Oh, Ji Wook...

31:29.690 --> 31:32.040
He called several times.

31:34.110 --> 31:36.260
<i>The phone is turned off...</i>

31:36.260 --> 31:38.050
That's weird.

31:38.050 --> 31:40.830
His phone is turned off.

31:51.500 --> 31:56.100
<i>I put on clean socks this morning...</i>

31:56.100 --> 31:58.590
<i>Mine?</i>

31:58.590 --> 32:01.080
<i>Yeah, mine too.</i>

32:01.080 --> 32:04.770
<i>- Where do you think this happened?
- I don't know...</i>

32:04.770 --> 32:08.000
<i>It must have been
