32:08.000 --> 32:10.390
<i>We should have helped him clean up.</i>

32:10.390 --> 32:13.810
<i>Yeah, it didn't look that dirty...</i>

32:15.390 --> 32:17.470
Oh my goodness...

32:20.080 --> 32:23.860
Excuse me, what did you just say?

32:23.860 --> 32:25.750
About what?

32:25.750 --> 32:29.380
We're here as witnesses
for that earlier case...

32:29.380 --> 32:32.420
No, what were you saying
about dirty socks?

32:32.420 --> 32:37.560
Oh, we were saying that we should
have helped him clean his house.

32:37.560 --> 32:41.690
These socks were clean this morning,
but look how dirty they got.

32:41.690 --> 32:44.330
<i>That much dust in a house
of someone with rhinitis?</i>

32:44.330 --> 32:47.140
<i>- Show me the wound.
- Wait...</i>

32:47.140 --> 32:49.120
<i>- What's wrong?
- I have rhinitis.</i>

32:49.120 --> 32:51.180
<i>It bothers me when the air gets stuffy.</i>

32:51.180 --> 32:54.500
<i>He held his breath whenever
the female officer got near.</i>

32:54.500 --> 32:57.050
<i>Director, I looked into
what you asked before.</i>

32:57.050 --> 33:03.140
There's a chance Yum Gi Tae may have
one of the worst types of pedophilia.

33:03.140 --> 33:06.170
<i>They usually approach children
by playing games or singing songs.</i>

33:06.170 --> 33:09.270
<i>The parents find out about the
assault late, making the arrest hard.</i>

33:12.690 --> 33:16.180
<i>They may appear very normal,
but when they get attracted to a child</i>

33:16.180 --> 33:18.070
they become abnormally
obsessed and sadistic.

33:18.070 --> 33:21.250
<i>There have been cases abroad where
victims have been tortured and murdered.</i>

33:21.250 --> 33:22.970
<i>What's suspicious about
Yum Gi Tae is that</i>

33:22.970 --> 33:26.130
during the rape, he clipped
Hee Joo's fingernails and toenails.

33:26.130 --> 33:31.800
<i>He denied it, but the parents said
they never clipped her nails that short.</i>

33:31.800 --> 33:35.750
And there is also a recording of him
imitating the voice of a child.

33:35.750 --> 33:39.130
<i>We can't conclude for sure that he's
a preferential pedophile from just this</i>

33:39.130 --> 33:42.630
<i>but they have been used as
circumstantial evidence abroad.</i>

33:42.630 --> 33:44.600
<i>The voice of a child?</i>

33:45.230 --> 33:48.040
<i>Then...</i>

33:49.390 --> 33:52.300
<i>I'll play with little Hee Joo.</i>

33:52.300 --> 33:54.560
<i>Little Hee Joo...</i>

34:01.800 --> 34:04.700
- What's going on?
- I need to talk to you.

34:09.300 --> 34:11.760
Yum Gi Tae doesn't have rhinitis.

34:11.760 --> 34:15.100
He was holding his breath because he
doesn't like the scent of a grown female.

34:15.100 --> 34:16.690
What?

34:16.690 --> 34:18.500
<i>Oh my goodness, blood...</i>

34:20.219 --> 34:22.420
I'm okay.

34:22.420 --> 34:26.320
- That's why he did that...
- There's one more thing.

34:26.320 --> 34:28.710
When he closed the door before,
he said in a child's voice

34:28.710 --> 34:32.219
"I'll play with little Hee Joo."

34:32.219 --> 34:36.110
- "Little Hee Joo"?
- I'm sure he's plotting something.

34:36.110 --> 34:39.280
Little Hee Joo...
Who is he referring to?

34:46.500 --> 34:47.710
Ji Wook.

34:47.710 --> 34:51.130
I'm sure he was mad thinking
Hee Joo sent him to jail

34:51.130 --> 34:53.790
and was plotting to get revenge
as soon as he got out.

34:53.790 --> 34:58.400
But Hee Joo's too old
for him to feel an attraction...

34:58.400 --> 35:01.020
so he's going for Ji Wook.

35:01.020 --> 35:03.260
If he's been thinking
about this since prison

35:03.260 --> 35:06.180
he can do something
even worse to Ji Wook.

35:07.000 --> 35:11.790
Agent Park, track Hwang Ji Wook's cell
phone and Yum Gi Tae's anklet.

35:12.550 --> 35:17.860
