35:28.230 --> 35:29.970
Hear anything about a stowaway?

35:29.970 --> 35:32.080
- Not sure...
- Yes, Kang Woo.

35:32.080 --> 35:34.670
Do you know a broker
who unlocks GPS anklets?

35:34.670 --> 35:38.360
