and they said he left a while ago.

36:20.280 --> 36:23.120
He's not picking up his phone,
and he didn't go to the store, either.

36:23.120 --> 36:27.410
- He's got nowhere to go.
- What was he wearing today?

36:27.410 --> 36:31.480
Let's see... A blue shirt.

36:32.600 --> 36:34.600
And beige pants.

36:34.600 --> 36:36.450
- Why do you ask?
- What happened to Ji Wook?

36:36.450 --> 36:38.990
- What's going on?
- Did something happen to him?

36:38.990 --> 36:42.420
We're a little worried,
so we've dispatched a team.

36:42.420 --> 36:48.060
One more question, have you noticed
anything different about Ji Wook lately?

36:48.060 --> 36:51.670
- Anyone he's gotten close to?
- Well...

36:51.670 --> 36:58.120
He started drawing a secret friend
since a few days ago.

37:08.610 --> 37:10.630
What's going on?

37:14.190 --> 37:16.190
Okay, thank you.

37:18.350 --> 37:20.780
Captain Do, it's a clown.

37:20.780 --> 37:23.940
Yum Gi Tae's approaching Ji Wook
dressed as a clown.

37:23.940 --> 37:26.190
