37:39.070 --> 37:41.500
It's cotton I used to clean up a wound.

37:41.500 --> 37:43.370
<i>It was the clown's nose.</i>

37:43.510 --> 37:47.240
Director, I saw an air pump
by the trash can in his house.

37:47.240 --> 37:49.290
<i>He probably used it to disguise himself.</i>

37:53.060 --> 37:55.370
We'll let you know when we find out more.

37:55.370 --> 37:57.720
I know you are worried,
but please wait.

37:58.730 --> 38:03.990
I think Yum Gi Tae's taken Ji Wook.

38:07.400 --> 38:09.380
Look here.

38:09.380 --> 38:14.670
The clown's fingers
look like crawling snakes.

38:14.670 --> 38:18.940
I know what this feels like.

38:19.810 --> 38:23.400
Even when I'm eating...
Even when I'm sleeping...

38:23.400 --> 38:29.340
It feels like the snakes
are crawling all over me.

38:53.500 --> 38:57.000
I feel the snakes crawl
all over my body all day.

38:58.190 --> 38:59.900
I know how that feels.

39:03.790 --> 39:06.000
Hee Joo.

39:06.000 --> 39:08.900
I promise you that we'll save him.

39:18.320 --> 39:23.500
Director, there's been
two non-residents leaving the villa.

39:23.500 --> 39:27.840
The one on the left looks suspicious.
It seems he's blown in air to appear fat.

39:27.840 --> 39:29.600
<i>Captain Do is right.</i>

39:29.600 --> 39:34.180
This is a code zero situation.
Near Dream Child Daycare in Gyeyoung

39:34.180 --> 39:38.610
a child named Hwang Ji Wook has been
kidnapped by a child rapist, Yum Gi Tae.

39:38.610 --> 39:41.740
It's likely Yum Gi Tae has removed
his GPS anklet to roam around freely.

39:41.740 --> 39:44.830
He's a pedophile who fulfills
his sexual fantasies on children.

39:44.830 --> 39:47.610
He must have plotted this out
through the last six years in prison.

39:47.610 --> 39:50.750
If we don't rescue him soon,
the boy's life may be in danger.

39:50.750 --> 39:52.290
Please hurry.

39:52.790 --> 39:56.750
What's this?
That bastard took Ji Wook?

39:58.000 --> 39:59.940
Damn!

40:07.310 --> 40:09.050
<i>We need to find them quickly.</i>

40:09.050 --> 40:13.580
<i>If anything happens to Ji Wook,
his family won't be able to handle it.</i>

40:13.580 --> 40:15.860
<i>The day Yum Gi Tae
came to the fish store</i>

40:15.860 --> 40:18.860
<i>she said his shoes were
