40:25.680 --> 40:29.360
- Hee Joo was raped by the beach, right?
- Yes, an abandoned house near the beach.

40:29.360 --> 40:31.420
Check the CCTVs around there.

40:32.100 --> 40:34.100
To all agents...

40:34.100 --> 40:36.720
Seven-year-old Hwang Ji Wook
has been kidnapped.

40:36.720 --> 40:41.630
Please assist in the search of all CCTVs
from the fish market to the sea.

40:43.550 --> 40:44.970
<i>According to Mrs. Oh Soo Nim</i>

40:44.970 --> 40:48.920
<i>Yum Gi Tae came to her store wearing
muddy shoes a few days ago.</i>

40:48.920 --> 40:52.210
<i>Perhaps he had gone out to
