41:19.460 --> 41:20.560
Yes, Sir.

41:20.560 --> 41:25.360
<i>Seven-year-old Hwang Ji Wook
has been kidnapped in the vicinity.</i>

41:25.360 --> 41:29.280
<i>Exact location, 136-36.
