41:30.190 --> 41:32.670
<i>Please hurry.</i>

41:40.080 --> 41:43.000
Wow, it's a clown.

41:43.000 --> 41:45.550
Play with me, Mr. Clown.

41:49.050 --> 41:51.100
I'll...

41:53.790 --> 41:55.900
play with you next time.

41:55.900 --> 41:57.740
