43:36.500 --> 43:39.500
Director, near the sea,
there is a sashimi center

43:39.500 --> 43:42.100
that closed due to resident objection,
right by the mudflats.

43:42.100 --> 43:44.420
Director, we found a clown.

43:46.600 --> 43:49.700
This is the call center.
A clown we presume to be Yum Gi Tae

43:49.700 --> 43:52.110
- has entered a sashimi center.
- What?

43:52.110 --> 43:55.830
<i>Please divide up the team,
and search the building.</i>

43:56.500 --> 43:59.100
Dispatch team will head in,
the rest of you stay on standby.

43:59.100 --> 44:00.600
Yes.

44:00.600 --> 44:04.500
<i>[5:30 p.m., 15 minutes into
the child kidnapping case at Gyeyoung]</i>

44:34.290 --> 44:36.000
Ji Wook.

44:45.290 --> 44:47.440
Where am I?

44:59.190 --> 45:04.500
We will start playing a very fun game.

45:04.500 --> 45:06.690
It's called...

45:08.400 --> 45:10.420
"Let's Become Adults."

45:10.420 --> 45:12.830
I don't want to play that game.

45:12.830 --> 45:16.400
My mom will be worried.

45:16.400 --> 45:18.400
I want to go home.

45:20.100 --> 45:21.330
Why?

45:21.330 --> 45:24.760
Don't you want to
become like your sister?

45:25.770 --> 45:28.590
Your sister used to be so pretty.

45:28.590 --> 45:32.960
And we used to be lovers.

45:33.600 --> 45:37.400
But she's grown up too much,
so we had to break up.

45:39.600 --> 45:43.340
So you'll have to replace her, okay?

45:45.050 --> 45:47.780
Hee Joo...

45:51.430 --> 45:54.170
Damn it.

45:59.780 --> 46:06.290
If it weren't for that bitch Hee Joo,
I would have become a good teacher.

46:06.290 --> 46:09.070
A teacher like a friend.

46:12.500 --> 46:15.050
Should we play now?

46:18.000 --> 46:21.000
<i>The building has at least
five sections on each floor.</i>

46:21.000 --> 46:24.240
<i>Yum Gi Tae must have rehearsed this
sick crime in his head over and over.</i>

46:24.240 --> 46:26.290
<i>I'm sure he'll be quick
without hesitation.</i>

46:26.290 --> 46:29.380
We'll each take a section,
and open up every door.

46:29.380 --> 46:33.290
Call out Ji Wook's name loudly, and if
you feel he's in danger, fire your gun.

46:33.290 --> 46:35.670
- I'll take full responsibility.
- Yes, Sir.

46:35.680 --> 46:40.940
Ji Wook!

46:53.720 --> 46:56.140
- Ji Wook!
- Ji Wook!

46:56.140 --> 47:00.150
Ji Wook!

47:01.100 --> 47:02.560
Ji Wook!

47:04.310 --> 47:05.540
Ji Wook!

47:09.960 --> 47:12.210
Ji Wook! Ji Wook!

47:12.210 --> 47:14.560
Ji Wook!

47:16.650 --> 47:18.010
Ji Wook!

47:20.160 --> 47:21.420
Ji Wook!

47:50.030 --> 47:53.690
Mister... Mister...

47:53.690 --> 47:55.740
You're so pretty.

47:57.100 --> 48:00.900
A pretty girl...

48:01.790 --> 48:04.320
needs to have
clean hands and feet, right?

48:06.040 --> 48:08.350
No...

48:12.100 --> 48:13.720
Ji Wook.

48:15.360 --> 48:16.690
Hey.

48:34.650 --> 48:37.640
<i>Ji Wook!</i>

48:39.590 --> 48:41.610
Here... I'm here!

48:46.900 --> 48:50.250
- How did they know I'm here?
<i>- Ji Wook!</i>

48:50.250 --> 48:51.560
Ji Wook!

49:01.000 --> 49:02.470
Ji Wook...

49:02.470 --> 49:03.500
Ji Wook!

49:27.010 --> 49:32.210
Either Ji Wook is unconscious, or he's
in a situation where he can't answer.

49:32.890 --> 49:35.130
<i>We need more clues.</i>

49:41.000 --> 49:42.610
Director!

49:42.610 --> 49:44.560
- I need to see her.
- No.

49:44.560 --> 49:46.430
Please... Director!

49:48.080 --> 49:50.640
- Ji Wook has an invincible watch.
- An invincible watch?

49:52.500 --> 49:56.210
He gave it to me
for my birthday last year.

49:58.330 --> 49:59.980
<i>It's just a regular toy.</i>

49:59.980 --> 50:04.400
<i>Every night, I would scream
because of the nightmares</i>

50:04.400 --> 50:07.900
so he broke his piggy bank
to buy that for me.

50:09.230 --> 50:13.290
Hee Joo, whenever the monster comes out

50:13.290 --> 50:17.000
if you press the button and say,
"Summon! Invincible Watch!"

50:17.000 --> 50:19.900
the monster will disappear.

50:23.070 --> 50:26.600
Hey! I told you not to bug me.

50:26.600 --> 50:28.590
Get out. Get out now.

50:32.900 --> 50:39.210
<i>He may be too scared to remember
that he has the watch on...</i>

50:39.210 --> 50:41.130
So Ji Wook's wearing the watch right now?

50:41.130 --> 50:43.240
- Yes.
- Okay.

50:43.240 --> 50:44.640
Director.

50:44.640 --> 50:49.450
I don't want Ji Wook to go through
the same nightmares I went through.

50:49.450 --> 50:55.400
Director, please, find him and save him.

50:55.400 --> 50:56.720
Just hold on a little bit, okay?

50:59.050 --> 51:00.100
Please...

51:12.500 --> 51:15.690
Ji Wook!

51:22.500 --> 51:23.920
<i>Invincible Watch.</i>

51:23.920 --> 51:25.690
Ji Wook believed a cartoon character

51:25.690 --> 51:28.400
would protect his sister
from her nightmares

51:28.400 --> 51:30.400
- and he's wearing that watch now.
<i>- What?</i>

51:30.400 --> 51:31.990
Make the watch work?

51:31.990 --> 51:35.740
<i>Yes. Turn the radio on
so I can hear where it is.</i>

51:42.510 --> 51:43.720
Okay.

51:44.290 --> 51:45.900
<i>Ji Wook!</i>

51:46.690 --> 51:48.330
Can you hear me?

51:50.110 --> 51:52.250
If you can hear me...

51:53.140 --> 51:55.650
can you summon Invincible Watch?

51:59.100 --> 52:01.600
<i>In order for me to catch the monster...</i>

52:02.600 --> 52:04.750
<i>I need your help!</i>

52:07.100 --> 52:08.690
Ji Wook!

52:09.860 --> 52:12.380
I'll help you!

52:13.000 --> 52:15.710
Please summon Invincible Watch!

52:16.740 --> 52:17.990
Ji Wook!

52:19.760 --> 52:21.590
Can you hear me?

52:23.400 --> 52:25.540
Ji Wook!

53:01.610 --> 53:03.920
Mister...

53:03.920 --> 53:09.470
Are you that mean monster that
comes out in my sister's dreams?

53:09.480 --> 53:16.600
I'm going to punish...

53:16.600 --> 53:18.350
Monster?

53:18.350 --> 53:20.400
Who says I'm a monster?

53:20.400 --> 53:24.890
I'm an angel who made
a love vow with your sister.

53:24.890 --> 53:28.180
I had no idea that bitch
would betray me.

53:28.180 --> 53:30.420
<i>- Ji Wook!
- Ji Wook!</i>

53:31.790 --> 53:34.630
<i>- Ji Wook!
- Ji Wook!</i>

53:36.400 --> 53:38.520
- Ji Wook!
- Ji Wook!

53:38.840 --> 53:42.680
- Your mom and sister are worried!
- Ji Wook, summon Invincible Watch!

53:42.680 --> 53:44.210
- Ji Wook!
- Ji Wook!

53:44.210 --> 53:47.040
I need your help.
Can you help us?

53:47.040 --> 53:53.820
- Ji Wook!
- Ji Wook!

53:53.820 --> 53:55.500
Ji Wook!

54:16.480 --> 54:18.390
Hee Joo...

54:18.390 --> 54:25.180
I'll protect you, Hee Joo...

54:25.180 --> 54:28.940
I'll...

54:44.600 --> 54:48.120
<i>I know I heard something.</i>

54:54.100 --> 54:55.820
Captain Do, I heard it.

54:55.820 --> 54:58.770
<i>It was for a short while,
but I heard a melody.</i>

55:04.100 --> 55:05.630
It's right next to you.

55:19.060 --> 55:20.200
Right here!

55:30.250 --> 55:31.860
Ji Wook! Ji Wook!

55:46.390 --> 55:47.750
Bastard.

55:47.750 --> 55:48.880
Where's Ji Wook?

55:48.880 --> 55:50.290
Where is he?

56:00.290 --> 56:01.970
Get him!

56:04.290 --> 56:05.290
Hey!

56:11.190 --> 56:13.080
Ji Wook.

56:13.080 --> 56:15.640
Ji Wook, are you okay?

56:15.640 --> 56:18.020
<i>- He's breathing.
- Ji Wook.</i>

56:23.600 --> 56:24.800
Get back!

56:40.000 --> 56:41.100
Yum Gi Tae.

56:41.100 --> 56:45.650
You are under arrest for kidnapping,
child sexual abuse, and attempted murder.

56:45.650 --> 56:49.100
You have the right to an attorney,
and the right to defend yourself.

56:49.100 --> 56:52.460
You're finished, asshole.

56:53.060 --> 56:57.670
<i>We're at the crime scene, we have
successfully arrested the suspect.</i>

57:11.640 --> 57:15.290
Ji Wook. Ji Wook, are you okay?

57:20.500 --> 57:22.400
Ji Wook.

57:22.400 --> 57:24.190
I'm sorry I took so long.

57:25.000 --> 57:26.500
It's all finished now.

57:28.230 --> 57:31.690
Mister...

57:31.690 --> 57:36.560
It was that monster that's
been hurting my sister, right?

57:36.560 --> 57:43.530
I took care of him,
so he won't came back again, right?

57:45.100 --> 57:50.010
Yeah, he'll never come back again.

57:50.010 --> 57:51.610
Never.

57:51.610 --> 57:53.450
Good job, Ji Wook.

57:53.450 --> 57:59.310
I want to see Mom, Dad, and Hee Joo.

58:02.000 --> 58:07.060
Okay, I'll take you home.

58:09.050 --> 58:10.620
<i>[5:50 p.m.]</i>

58:10.620 --> 58:13.100
<i>[Child kidnapping case
at Gyeyoung is closed]</i>

58:14.190 --> 58:18.420
Ji Wook's been safely rescued.

58:20.310 --> 58:22.580
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

58:23.050 --> 58:25.160
It's all thanks to you.

58:25.160 --> 58:30.310
It's because you went to his house
this morning that we could catch on.

58:31.500 --> 58:37.060
And it's because you opened up that we
were able to miraculously find Ji Wook.

58:40.730 --> 58:48.110
It took this painful incident to show
that pedophiles can't be let off easy.

58:48.110 --> 58:51.600
As a police officer, I apologize.

58:55.790 --> 59:01.710
We will do our best so that
Yum Gi Tae is never released from prison.

59:01.710 --> 59:06.900
You've been sending us signals
and asking for help.

59:08.100 --> 59:10.100
I'm sorry it took so long.

59:11.290 --> 59:12.600
Thank you.

59:13.100 --> 59:16.290
Thank you.

59:17.480 --> 59:19.350
Thank you.

59:19.350 --> 59:22.250
Please go hug Hee Joo.

59:22.520 --> 59:24.050
Hee Joo.

59:30.100 --> 59:34.150
- Come on, let go of me...
- Shut up and go!

59:34.150 --> 59:36.120
Damn it!

59:36.120 --> 59:41.110
What wrong did I do?

59:41.110 --> 59:43.930
This bastard...

59:43.930 --> 59:48.130
You don't know what you did wrong?
You're not human, are you?

59:48.130 --> 59:49.900
You want a beatdown?

59:52.190 --> 59:54.600
Don't get too emotional.

59:56.190 --> 59:58.310
You won't do anything
about this bastard, then?

59:58.950 --> 01:00:01.500
Go down first.

01:00:01.500 --> 01:00:03.730
I'll bring him down.

01:00:07.400 --> 01:00:09.250
Let's go.

01:00:09.250 --> 01:00:10.590
Come on.

01:00:11.120 --> 01:00:14.730
- Am I the bad guy here?
- Come on...

01:00:23.100 --> 01:00:26.190
I see you are much more classy, Captain.

01:00:36.100 --> 01:00:39.950
That's it? That's it, asshole?

01:00:39.950 --> 01:00:41.540
A clown?

01:00:41.540 --> 01:00:45.760
Putting makeup on your face
won't get rid of your rotting stench.

01:00:45.760 --> 01:00:49.250
Even if you get a new face,
people like you won't change.

01:00:49.250 --> 01:00:54.700
You better hope you get killed in prison.

01:00:54.700 --> 01:00:56.770
Otherwise, I'll kill you.

01:00:58.400 --> 01:01:00.060
Yes, sir.

01:01:01.500 --> 01:01:03.700
But do you know?

01:01:04.900 --> 01:01:06.750
Because you stopped me

01:01:06.750 --> 01:01:10.080
I may get out in a few years,
since it was only an attempt.

01:01:10.080 --> 01:01:14.320
So tell Ji Wook
to wait just a little bit.

01:01:14.320 --> 01:01:17.890
Next time, I'll make sure
we have a lot of fun together.

01:01:19.340 --> 01:01:22.210
I'll show you what fun is.

01:01:23.450 --> 01:01:25.950
- Damn it.
- Be careful.

01:01:29.790 --> 01:01:32.790
You bastard, are you crazy?

01:01:34.640 --> 01:01:37.560
Are you okay?
There are two more flights.

01:01:39.650 --> 01:01:42.900
Detective, sir...

01:01:54.530 --> 01:01:57.110
Get him in the car.
It's just a little bruise.

01:01:57.110 --> 01:01:58.510
Yes, Sir.

01:01:58.510 --> 01:02:01.600
- Come on.
- Let go!

01:02:17.000 --> 01:02:18.710
Thank you, everyone.

01:02:18.710 --> 01:02:22.800
Please don't forget that
we're on the front lines of crime.

01:02:22.800 --> 01:02:24.850
We may only be here for a month

01:02:24.850 --> 01:02:28.290
but I wish for our team
to continue to grow.

01:02:28.290 --> 01:02:30.120
Thank you.

01:02:37.960 --> 01:02:39.680
- Director Kang.
- Yeah?

01:02:39.680 --> 01:02:44.920
Detective Koo just called saying
Captain Do taught Yum Gi Tae a lesson.

01:02:44.920 --> 01:02:48.120
I don't think he's as bad as the rumors.

01:02:48.120 --> 01:02:51.210
- And this.
- Thanks.

01:03:07.430 --> 01:03:09.600
My baby.

01:03:09.600 --> 01:03:11.820
Are you okay?

01:03:11.820 --> 01:03:12.970
You're not hurt?

01:03:12.970 --> 01:03:20.190
Yeah, I destroyed the monster
with the Invincible Watch from Hee Joo.

01:03:20.190 --> 01:03:21.590
Good job.

01:03:21.590 --> 01:03:24.180
I'm so proud of you, Ji Wook.

01:03:26.180 --> 01:03:30.660
Do you know how worried I was?
Why would you follow a stranger?

01:03:36.560 --> 01:03:39.590
- There's Hee Joo's mom...
- Soo Nim.

01:03:39.590 --> 01:03:41.970
You must have been so worried.
Are you okay?

01:03:41.970 --> 01:03:46.060
- How horrible.
- He'll rot in prison forever...

01:03:46.060 --> 01:03:49.820
You must have been scared.
We'll protect you, don't worry.

01:03:49.820 --> 01:03:57.830
- You must have been so worried.
- I respect you so much for your bravery.

01:05:09.600 --> 01:05:11.290
Excuse me.

01:05:11.290 --> 01:05:12.810
You have a phone call.

01:05:16.400 --> 01:05:17.750
Thanks.

01:05:28.790 --> 01:05:31.870
<i>[For child sex offenses, the U.S.
has a minimum sentence of 25 years]</i>

01:05:31.870 --> 01:05:35.510
<i>[France has 20 years, England has a life
sentence, and China, the death penalty.]</i>

01:05:35.510 --> 01:05:38.690
<i>[Korea also has penalties, but nothing
that reflects the gravity of the crime.]</i>

01:05:38.690 --> 01:05:41.900
<i>[Victims suffer throughout their life,
and a tougher punishment is needed.]</i>

01:05:41.900 --> 01:05:44.820
<i>[A lenient punishment only increases
the second offense rate.]</i>

01:05:44.820 --> 01:05:48.000
<i>[Offenders must be warned by banning
them from returning to society.]</i>

01:05:48.000 --> 01:05:55.000
Subtitles by DramaFever

01:06:10.200 --> 01:06:11.630
Yes, Captain Do.

01:06:11.630 --> 01:06:14.690
<i>I'm at the motel
where Kwak Min Soo was.</i>

01:06:14.690 --> 01:06:17.600
I think he's the culprit.

01:06:17.600 --> 01:06:20.280
What? Are you sure?

01:06:20.280 --> 01:06:23.640
There are pictures of corpses.

01:06:40.900 --> 01:06:44.290
And there's the mask he wore, too.

01:06:45.290 --> 01:06:48.100
Everything is here.

01:06:49.050 --> 01:06:51.790
Kwak Min Soo was trying to
smuggle himself out on a ship

01:06:51.790 --> 01:06:53.690
<i>and he was caught by
coast guards on duty.</i>
